expression.expression-string: "SELECT to_json(ent) AS entity, attributes.data AS attrs FROM groups ent JOIN (SELECT id, json_agg(json_build_object('name', attr_name, 'value', COALESCE(attr_value, attr_value_text), 'type', type)) AS data FROM group_attr_values av JOIN attr_names an ON av.attr_id = an.id GROUP BY group_id) AS attributes ON ent.id = attributes.id WHERE ent.vo_id = :1"
